Package ides.api.model.supeventset

Interface SupEventSetPublisher

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SupervisoryEventSet
    public interface SupEventSetPublisher
    A publisher of SupervisoryEventSet messages.

    • Method Detail

      • addSubscriber

        void addSubscriber​(SupEventSetSubscriber subscriber)
        Attaches the given subscriber to this publisher. The given subscriber will receive notifications of changes from this publisher.
        Parameters:
        subscriber - the subscriber to be attached

      • fireSupEventSetChanged

        void fireSupEventSetChanged​(SupEventSetMessage message)
        Triggers a notification to all subscribers that the event set has changed.
        Parameters:
        message - message with additional information about the change.

      • getSupEventSetSubscribers

        SupEventSetSubscriber[] getSupEventSetSubscribers()
        Returns all current subscribers to this publisher.
        Returns:
        all current subscribers to this publisher.

      • removeSubscriber

        void removeSubscriber​(SupEventSetSubscriber subscriber)
        Removes the given subscriber to this publisher. The given subscriber will no longer receive notifications of changes from this publisher.
        Parameters:
        subscriber - the subscriber to be removed
